AbstractFactory
public class ConcreteFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbstractFactory

The Scheduler typically needs only one instance of a ConcreteFactory per component family. So it is usually best implemented as a Singleton.

Author:
Hagen Mahnke, Konrad Reiche
